A letter sent from Col. John Disbrowe, dated December 29. 1659. Superscribed, to the Right Honorable, the Speaker of the Parliament of this Common-wealth, these present, at Westminster. Read in Parliament, December 30. 1659. Desborough, John, 1608-1680.
6, [2] p.
printed by John Streater, and John Macock, London : 1659.
